---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';

// Import images
import AboutHeroImage1 from '../assets/members1.jpeg';
import AboutHeroImage2 from '../assets/members2.jpeg'; 
---

<Layout
    title="Who We Are"
    description="Learn about the history, mission, and team behind Mision 21"
    pubDate={new Date('January 05 2025')}
>

    <div class="hero-carousel-container">
        <div class="carousel-slide active fade">
            <img src={AboutHeroImage1.src} alt="Mission 21 Team" />
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-slide fade">
            <img src={AboutHeroImage2.src} alt="Mission 21 Community" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="intro-section mobile-centered">
        <div class="mission-header">
            <h2>Our History</h2>
            <div class="text-content">
                <p class="lead-text">
                    <strong>Mision 21</strong> was born from a dream: to reclaim our communities.
                </p>
                <p>
                    It all began with the vision of our founder, <strong>Luis Satoshi</strong>, who yearned to find a real and tangible way to reach those territories that, for years, were dominated by violence and gangs. His desire was not just to enter, but to transform: to restore hope and freedom to those who had lived in fear.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Today, that vision is a reality. Mision 21 works actively to bring <strong>financial freedom</strong> through Bitcoin, teach <strong>Christian values</strong> that restore the spirit, and promote sports through <strong>soccer schools</strong>, allowing children and youth to exchange environments of violence for spaces of recreation and healthy growth.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pillars-container">
            <div class="pillar">
                <i class="fa-brands fa-bitcoin"></i>
                <h4>Financial Freedom</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-cross"></i>
                <h4>Christian Values</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-futbol"></i>
                <h4>Sports and Prevention</h4>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <section class="team-section mobile-centered">
        <h2>Our Leadership</h2>
        <p class="team-intro">
            Behind every action is a team committed to operational and spiritual excellence, structured to ensure long-term impact.
        </p>

        <h3 class="team-category">Board of Directors and Executives</h3>
        
        <div class="team-wrapper">
            <div class="team-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h4>Luis Satoshi</h4>
                    <span class="role">Founder & Chief Visionary Officer (CVO)</span>
                    <p>
                        He is the moral and strategic compass of the organization. His role is to safeguard the foundational philosophy and project the future of the mission.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="team-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h4>Irving</h4>
                    <span class="role">Chief Operating Officer (COO)</span>
                    <p>
                        The principal executor of the vision. He is in charge of operational excellence, ensuring the organization runs with precision and efficiency.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="team-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h4>Diego</h4>
                    <span class="role">Chief Technology & Innovation Officer (CTO)</span>
                    <p>
                        He leads the digital transformation, managing everything from Bitcoin mining operations to the formalization of educational alliances.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="team-category">Area Directors</h3>
        
        <div class="team-wrapper">
            <div class="team-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h4>Maricela</h4>
                    <span class="role">Director of Children's Christian Education</span>
                    <p>
                        She leads children's education. Her focus is directing biblical education programs and values designed exclusively for children.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="team-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h4>Wiliam</h4>
                    <span class="role">Director of Social Prevention & Family</span>
                    <p>
                        He manages preventive social impact. He executes strategies in schools and develops the School for Parents to strengthen the family core.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="team-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h4>Antony</h4>
                    <span class="role">Director of Theology & Creative Media</span>
                    <p>
                        An integral role that cares for the spiritual health of the team and public image. Responsible for theological content and media management.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <section class="volunteers-section mobile-centered">
        <div class="volunteer-box">
            <h3>Volunteer Corps</h3>
            <p>
                Mision 21 would not be possible without our volunteer corps. They are committed individuals who provide essential operational and logistical support in every activity we carry out on the ground.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>

<script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        let slideIndex = 0;
        const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".carousel-slide");
        const intervalTime = 4000; 

        function showSlides() {
            if(slides.length === 0) return;
            slides.forEach(slide => slide.classList.remove("active"));
            slideIndex++;
            if (slideIndex > slides.length) { slideIndex = 1 }
            slides[slideIndex - 1].classList.add("active");
            setTimeout(showSlides, intervalTime); 
        }

        if (slides.length > 0) {
            setTimeout(showSlides, intervalTime);
        }
    });
</script>

<style>
    /* --- CAROUSEL --- */
    .hero-carousel-container {
        width: 100%;
        position: relative;
        height: 400px; 
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    .carousel-slide {
        display: none;
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        top: 0; left: 0;
    }

    .carousel-slide.active { display: block; }

    .carousel-slide img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .fade { animation: fade 1.5s; }
    @keyframes fade { from {opacity: 0.4} to {opacity: 1} }

    /* --- GENERAL TEXT STYLES --- */
    p {
        color: #ccc; 
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    h2, h3, h4, strong { color: #fff; }

    h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: left; }

    .lead-text {
        font-size: 1.3em;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
        font-weight: 300;
    }

    .divider {
        border: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); 
        margin: 4rem 0;
    }

    /* --- PILLARS --- */
    .pillars-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        margin: 3rem 0;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .pillar {
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 150px;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .pillar i {
        font-size: 3rem;
        color: #F7931A; 
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    
    .pillar:hover i { transform: scale(1.1); }
    .pillar h4 { font-weight: 700; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

    /* --- TEAM --- */
    .team-section { margin-top: 2rem; }
    
    .team-intro {
        text-align: left; 
        max-width: 700px;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        color: #aaa;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .team-category {
        color: #F7931A;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #F7931A;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        text-align: left;
    }

    /* Use flexbox for the team wrapper by default for PC too (grid behavior) */
    .team-wrapper {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .team-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); 
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 2rem;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
        /* Ensures box-sizing doesn't break widths */
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .team-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        border-color: #F7931A;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .team-card h4 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.4rem; color: #fff; }

    .team-card .role {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #F7931A;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .team-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #ccc; margin: 0; }

    /* --- VOLUNTEERS --- */
    .volunteers-section {
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
        border: 1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 12px;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .volunteers-section h3 { color: #F7931A; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .volunteer-box p { margin: 0 auto; max-width: 800px; }

    /* =================================================================
       MOBILE AND TABLET SOLUTION (Max Width 900px)
       ================================================================= */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        
        /* 1. FORCED CENTERED TEXT */
        .mobile-centered h2, 
        .mobile-centered h3, 
        .mobile-centered p, 
        .mobile-centered .team-intro,
        .mobile-centered .team-category {
            text-align: center !important;
            margin-left: auto !important;
            margin-right: auto !important;
        }

        /* 2. REPAIR TEAM WRAPPER */
        .team-wrapper {
            display: flex !important; /* Change Grid to Flex */
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center; /* THIS CENTERS THE CHILDREN (CARDS) */
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0; /* Remove strange padding */
        }

        /* 3. REPAIR CARD (The left-side problem) */
        .team-card {
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 340px; /* A controlled width to float in the center */
            
            /* THE KEY: Auto margins on the sides */
            margin-left: auto !important;
            margin-right: auto !important;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* 4. PILLARS ADJUSTMENT */
        .pillars-container {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* 5. CAROUSEL ADJUSTMENT */
        .hero-carousel-container {
            height: 250px;
        }
    }
</style>